  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avi Games brings you the next part of the hidden object game \"Sweet Home: Look and Find\". Enjoy an even cozier collection of hidden-object tasks and mini games with <i>Sweet Home Look and Find 3</i>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax, get comfortable, and enjoy finding objects, solving puzzles, and conquering mini-games on an exciting journey to various places imbued with warmth and comfort! Take a walk in nature, sit by the pool, and even barbecue in the backyard! Use your skills and knowledge to find all the hidden objects and complete the mini-games as you kick back and challenge yourself in this blissful hidden-object game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Collector’s Edition includes:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eight new locations to find many more objects!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eight exclusive mini-games to challenge your skills!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring the cozy atmosphere into your own home with a handy music player!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check out a collection of beautiful downloadable wallpapers!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avi Games brings you the next part of the hidden object game \"Sweet Home: Look and Find\". Enjoy an even cozier collection of hidden-object tasks and mini games with <i>Sweet Home Look and Find 3</i>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax, get comfortable, and enjoy finding objects, solving puzzles, and conquering mini-games on an exciting journey to various places imbued with warmth and comfort! Take a walk in nature, sit by the pool, and even barbecue in the backyard! Use your skills and knowledge to find all the hidden objects and complete the mini-games as you kick back and challenge yourself in this blissful hidden-object game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Collector’s Edition includes:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eight new locations to find many more objects!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eight exclusive mini-games to challenge your skills!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring the cozy atmosphere into your own home with a handy music player!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check out a collection of beautiful downloadable wallpapers!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
